This paper deals with document retrieval, which is a subfield of information retrieval (IR) in computer science. The use of NLP tools to improve the initial ranking suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL) or natural language processing (cs.NE). The focus on improving the ranking using machine learning techniques suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the use of a search engine and the evaluation of the results suggest that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of computer and information science (cs.CC).
